Blak includes generated ASCII frame data and the source GIF asset for the black-hole splash.

Source artwork:
- Project: milli.nvim
- Repository: https://github.com/Amansingh-afk/milli.nvim
- Asset used: media/previews/blackhole.gif
- License: MIT, as stated by the milli.nvim repository.

The generated Lua frame table in lua/blak/splash/frames/blackhole.lua was produced from assets/blackhole.gif by scripts/generate_blackhole_frames.py. Blak does not vendor the milli.nvim plugin runtime.
